title: Yak and Yeti - Westminster
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Nepalese, Tibetan, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Himalayan cuisine (Nepal and Indian) and its own brewed beer; another outlet in Denver. All-you-can-eat buffet at lunchtime, a la carte menu dinner. While the menu is primarily meat, the website shows a vegetarian section with around 15 main dishes, and on premises you will also find a vegan menu. Note the samosas may contain dairy.
